Get_Sample_Type_Test
Public Sub Get_Sample_Type_Test()
Description

Function used to test if the function Sample_Type_Identifier.Get_Sample_Type is working

Test data are

  • A string array TestArray

Function will assert if Sample_Type_Identifier.Get_Sample_Type(TestArray) gives the same output as QCArray
